<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-10436] STC: closure parameter type-checking: declared vs inferred</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-10436</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Consider the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; java.util.function.Consumer

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;T&amp;gt; T m(Consumer&amp;lt;? &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;super&lt;/span&gt; T&amp;gt; c) {
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// ...
&lt;/span&gt;}
@groovy.transform.TypeChecked
void test() {
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.m { &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Number&lt;/span&gt; n -&amp;gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; big = n.toBigInteger()
  }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Recent fixes for closure param STC (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-8917&quot; title=&quot;Failed to infer parameter type of some SAM, e.g. BinaryOperator&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-8917&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-8917&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-10049&quot; title=&quot;STC fails when calling a generic method from another generic method&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-10049&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-10049&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-10053&quot; title=&quot;STC: Wrong type inferred for lambda parameter in a generic method&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-10053&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-10053&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, etc.) are producing an error for the param &quot;expected Object actual Number&quot; and an error for the call expression &quot;cannot find method Object#toBigInteger()&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;StaticTypeCheckingVisitor#inferClosureParamterTypes&lt;/tt&gt; does not use closure expressions to determine placeholder types and there are no other type witnesses.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
